race.description: Mcgrath Estate Agents Ballan Mdn Plate
race.comment: PAVLICH (6) as had three jumpouts in preparation for this and, through them, has shown not only a swift turn of foot but also an ability to take up a spot early. Looks beautifully drawn in barrier four and copuld be hard to go past in this. LION CITY EXPRESS (5) on debut. Coming along nicely leading into this, winning a Colac trial before placing in a Bendigo jump-out. Respect any market moves. INFINITE JEST (1) resuming from a spell. Placed in a recent Moe jump-out. Opened last campaign with an eighth at Pakenham over 1200m. In the mix. GORDEEVA (11) first-starter by Russian Camelot who was an AUD $ 18,000 (Inglis 2024 Premier Yearling Sale) purchase. Placed in latest jumpout and worth consideration.
